                class="callout-item"
                data-callout="1"
                id="c1-1"
                style="--i:1;">
                <b>1</b>
                Switch between editing content and task mode.</li>
              <li
                class="callout-item"
                data-callout="2"
                id="c1-2"
                style="--i:2;">
                <b>2</b>
                A focused panel to edit your page. No code required.</li>
              <li
